🌈 Embracing My Journey, Celebrating My Pride 🌈 - As #PrideMonth begins, my heart overflows with gratitude & reflection. It hasn’t always been an easy road, but as each year passes, I stand stronger & prouder than ever before. ✨

Something I don’t talk about enough is what growing up was like for me. I faced relentless bullying, cruel words & told to end my exsistence simply because I was “different”. Somehow, through it all, I found the courage to embrace my own identity & celebrate the uniqueness that sets me apart. 🥰 Day in & day out, I continued to cling on to hope because I had to believe that it would get better & now, looking back on it, I never could’ve imagined the journey that awaited me. 💕

Today, I am blessed to be married to the love of my life, a person who sees the true beauty within me & celebrates it every day. 👨🏼‍🤝‍👨🏻 I’ve had the fortunate opportunity to share my story on national television which has resonated with viewers around the world, something I don’t take lightly. 📺 And I’ve surrounded myself with a strong, vibrant, diverse & beautiful support system that pushes me to be the best version of myself & inspires me to keep being James, because I am enough. 💜🙏🏻

So, to anyone who has ever felt the sting of judgment, the weight of discrimination, or the despair of hopelessness, know that you are not alone. 🫶🏻 I offer you my unwavering support & love because your worth is immeasurable, your spirit is unbreakable & IT DOES GET BETTER. 🥳🏳️‍🌈 #Pride #GayPride #HappyPride

The one thing my (James) parents wanted to do on our trip to Hawaii was a helicopter tour… @bluehawaiianhelicopter didn’t disappoint! 🚁💙 It was our third tour with them but my parents first time ever being in a helicopter. 🥹✨

↔️ Swipe for the breathtaking highlights from our adventure! 📸

1️⃣ Manawaiopuna Falls: Witnessing the majestic Manawaiopuna Falls from above, known as “Jurassic Falls” (from Jurassic Park) was an absolute thrill! 🦖🦕
2️⃣ Waimea Canyon: Hawaii's Grand Canyon looked even grander from the skies! 🌄
3️⃣ Napali Coast: The rugged beauty of the Napali Coast left us speechless. An unforgettable sight! ⛰️🌊 

Blue Hawaiian Helicopters offers the best helicopter tours and sightseeing in Hawaii 🚁🏝️. If you ever visit Oahu, Maui, Kauai or the Big Island, don't miss this breathtaking experience - especially in Kauai,  the ultimate way to see the island! 🌺🚁🤙

🏨 Checking into paradise at the @princewaikiki! 🌺 A little #throwback to our unforgettable stay a month ago - the views from our room are forever engrained in our memory. 😍

Things we loved about #PrinceWaikiki 💜:

🏝️ It was centrally located to so much: the harbor, shopping, restaurants & three beaches, including the world famous #WaikikiBeach. 🏄‍♂️ 

🛏️ Their cozy & comfortable accommodations allowed us to make ourselves at home. The floor to ceiling windows allowed us to wake up & overlook paradise every morning! 🌅

🏊‍♂️ Plus, we can’t forget to mention the stunning infinity pool, with gorgeous views (especially during sunset) & their cabanas - the perfect spot to kick back & relax after a long day of exploring the island of #Oahu. 🏝️

If you’re ever visiting the Island of Oahu ☀️, we highly recommend booking a stay at this beautiful property! #tbt #ThrowbackThursday #Hotel #Travel #TravelTips
